# Real facts derived by materialize()-ing graph.n3 with this engine (a
# subset -- the full derived set is 23 triples; this is the ones that
# demonstrate the transitive-closure query goal from upstream's
# graph.filter.n3, `{:paris :path :nantes} => {:paris :path :nantes}.`,
# plus the generic rdfs:domain-driven typing of the :oneway/:path
# properties themselves).
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>.
@prefix : <http://www.agfa.com/w3c/euler/graph.axiom#>.

:oneway a rdf:Property.
:path a rdf:Property.
:paris :path :nantes.
:paris :path :tours.
:paris :path :orleans.
